1
00:00:04,980 --> 00:00:06,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My brother's...</font>

2
00:00:06,460 --> 00:00:09,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">rather, Gilbert's mansion 
has been searched.</font>

3
00:00:09,190 --> 00:00:11,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Documents connected to the 
plot to murder Your Majesty</font>

4
00:00:11,940 --> 00:00:14,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">were found hidden in rooms underground.</font>

5
00:00:15,410 --> 00:00:19,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. So they've found 
concrete evidence.</font>

6
00:00:17,490 --> 00:00:21,950
<font face="Times New Roman" size="18" color="#d7dad8"><b>{\an3}<font color="#efefeb">Albert Ararat 
<font size="13">Crown Prince, Second Prince</font></font></b></font>

7
00:00:19,450 --> 00:00:21,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That fool isn't even worthy 
of comparison to a dog.</font>

8
00:00:22,930 --> 00:00:25,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And what will be done with him?</font>

9
00:00:25,410 --> 00:00:28,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Premeditated murder of the 
emperor is undeniably treason.</font>

10
00:00:28,810 --> 00:00:32,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Under imperial law, there is no choice 
but to cut him in half at the waist.</font>

11
00:00:32,740 --> 00:00:34,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

12
00:00:35,500 --> 00:00:38,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However, this case could be perceived 
as merely attempted murder.</font>

13
00:00:39,690 --> 00:00:41,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And what would that entail?</font>

14
00:00:41,890 --> 00:00:44,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He isn't exempt from being cut in half,</font>

15
00:00:44,480 --> 00:00:47,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but he can still be granted the 
minimum stay of execution.</font>

16
00:00:47,980 --> 00:00:51,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">His sentence would then be carried out 
only when Your Majesty orders it.</font>

17
00:00:51,770 --> 00:00:54,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why complicate the matter like that?</font>

18
00:00:54,460 --> 00:00:56,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's still execution by cutting in half.</font>

19
00:00:56,580 --> 00:00:59,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If he's to be executed anyway, what 
does it matter when it's done?</font>

20
00:00:59,970 --> 00:01:02,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, Noah has yet again proven wise.</font>

21
00:01:02,350 --> 00:01:06,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He has considered this from both 
legal and emotional perspectives.</font>

22
00:01:06,600 --> 00:01:08,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I appreciate you giving it such thought.</font>

23
00:01:10,180 --> 00:01:12,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Gilbert is still the emperor's son.</i></font>

24
00:01:12,670 --> 00:01:16,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Keeping in mind that he might love 
him too much to execute him,</i></font>

25
00:01:16,650 --> 00:01:21,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I gave him an option that would 
essentially result in a life sentence.</i></font>

26
00:01:21,730 --> 00:01:23,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There is no need for hesitation.</font>

27
00:01:23,650 --> 00:01:28,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Those who attempted to kill you with 
poison deserve immediate death.</font>

28
00:01:30,590 --> 00:01:31,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Albert.</font>

29
00:01:32,380 --> 00:01:35,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I leave his execution in your hands. Go.</font>

30
00:01:35,490 --> 00:01:36,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sire.</font>

31
00:01:37,560 --> 00:01:40,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He really thought he could 
get his hands on the crown.</i></font>

32
00:01:40,540 --> 00:01:42,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Pitiful.</i></font>

33
00:01:45,170 --> 00:01:46,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Noah.</font>

34
00:01:46,910 --> 00:01:49,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were right to tell me that.</font>

35
00:01:49,060 --> 00:01:53,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How brilliant of you to show such 
consideration in these circumstances.</font>

36
00:01:53,610 --> 00:01:57,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel your consideration has 
brought some degree of salvation.</font>

37
00:01:57,450 --> 00:02:04,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Personally, I would like to transfer 
ownership of Gilbert's fief to you.</font>

38
00:02:04,350 --> 00:02:05,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mustn't.</font>

39
00:02:05,340 --> 00:02:06,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

40
00:02:06,960 --> 00:02:10,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I informed you of Gilbert's 
plot confidentially.</font>

41
00:02:11,400 --> 00:02:13,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I were to receive his fief now,</font>

42
00:02:13,590 --> 00:02:17,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">the other princes would start making 
all kinds of reports anonymously</font>

43
00:02:17,620 --> 00:02:20,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and sabotage each other in hopes 
of earning the same reward.</font>

44
00:02:20,490 --> 00:02:22,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, slow down.</font>

45
00:02:22,040 --> 00:02:24,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I only said I would <i>like</i> to do that.</font>

46
00:02:25,870 --> 00:02:28,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't mind my sons competing,</font>

47
00:02:28,250 --> 00:02:31,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I can't have them trying 
to sabotage each other.</font>

48
00:02:31,890 --> 00:02:35,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I will not reward you this time.</font>

49
00:02:35,400 --> 00:02:37,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I understand.</font>

50
00:02:37,600 --> 00:02:40,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Instead, I will merely do 
that which is expected.</font>

51
00:02:40,730 --> 00:02:43,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You will soon be relocating 
to your own fief.</font>

52
00:02:43,750 --> 00:02:47,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's time to start thinking 
about your future wife.</font>

53
00:02:47,810 --> 00:02:48,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sire.</font>

54
00:02:48,810 --> 00:02:53,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Engagement by age twelve is not 
unusual in the imperial family.</i></font>

55
00:02:53,790 --> 00:02:58,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And a prince's first wife—his legal 
wife, as opposed to a concubine—</i></font>

56
00:02:58,110 --> 00:03:00,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>is chosen for 100% political reasons,</i></font>

57
00:03:00,390 --> 00:03:03,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and must have standing 
befitting the role.</i></font>

58
00:03:04,250 --> 00:03:10,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>For that reason, the prince himself has 
essentially no say in who he marries.</i></font>

59
00:03:10,510 --> 00:03:15,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>However, it is possible 
for fate to play a part.</i></font>

60
00:03:16,000 --> 00:03:19,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How about the granddaughter of 
my uncle, the Lightning Prince?</font>

61
00:03:19,990 --> 00:03:21,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The Lightning Prince...</i></font>

62
00:03:21,530 --> 00:03:25,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I believe he's been retired and out 
of politics for many years already.</i></font>

63
00:03:26,280 --> 00:03:31,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Divination has revealed that you and 
she will have a very clever child.</font>

64
00:03:31,400 --> 00:03:34,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I would only place the 
probability around 1%,</font>

65
00:03:34,560 --> 00:03:38,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but that child may even be 
more brilliant than you.</font>

66
00:03:38,730 --> 00:03:43,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing would make me happier than to 
take someone so remarkable as my wife.</font>

67
00:03:46,790 --> 00:03:49,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case, I will initiate 
the marriage negotiations.</font>

68
00:03:49,910 --> 00:03:50,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, sire.</font>

69
00:03:58,850 --> 00:04:02,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My, Prince Noah never ceases to amaze.</font>

70
00:04:03,220 --> 00:04:08,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He didn't even know the girl's 
name or anything else about her.</font>

71
00:04:08,380 --> 00:04:11,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what it means to be a 
prince—part of an imperial family.</font>

72
00:04:11,550 --> 00:04:17,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">True, but it's natural for a young man 
to take an interest in his future wife.</font>

73
00:04:17,030 --> 00:04:19,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To get past that at such a young age...</font>

74
00:04:19,490 --> 00:04:21,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What can it be called but amazing?</font>

75
00:04:22,350 --> 00:04:24,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Choose a grandchild as your successor."</font>

76
00:04:24,650 --> 00:04:28,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"A good grandchild guarantees 
three generations of prosperity."</font>

77
00:04:28,970 --> 00:04:31,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It is indeed a good idea.</font>

78
00:04:31,750 --> 00:04:36,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But how likely is it, truly, that 
my grandchild could surpass me?</font>

79
00:04:36,060 --> 00:04:40,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">At the moment, all that potential 
lies with Prince Noah.</font>

80
00:04:40,590 --> 00:04:44,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If his brilliance passes 
down to his child...</font>

81
00:04:44,100 --> 00:04:45,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

82
00:04:46,480 --> 00:04:48,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All we can do is hope, then.</font>

83
00:05:04,610 --> 00:05:06,570
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#817c4f"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="10">Born Blessed, So I'll Obtain Ultimate Power</font></b></font></font></font>

84
00:05:04,610 --> 00:05:06,570
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#051529">m 0 0 l 235 0 l 225 8 l 235 15 l 18 15 l 30 8 l 18 0</font></font>

85
00:06:21,420 --> 00:06:23,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am resigned to my fate.</font>

86
00:06:23,730 --> 00:06:28,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I make no excuses for my betrayal of 
Prince Gilbert, my former master.</font>

87
00:06:28,300 --> 00:06:30,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please, at least, make it quick.</font>

88
00:06:30,470 --> 00:06:33,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't be so hasty. Who said any of that?</font>

89
00:06:33,710 --> 00:06:35,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">B-But...</font>

90
00:06:35,290 --> 00:06:38,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">People are treasures.
I don't kill them on a whim.</font>

91
00:06:38,580 --> 00:06:43,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And imperial law says an indicted man
who exposes treason is to be acquitted.</font>

92
00:06:43,440 --> 00:06:44,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

93
00:06:44,730 --> 00:06:47,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I called you here for a few reasons.</font>

94
00:06:47,960 --> 00:06:50,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">First, Gilbert has been executed,</font>

95
00:06:50,580 --> 00:06:53,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and all power he possessed has collapsed.</font>

96
00:06:53,080 --> 00:06:57,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So there's no longer any need for you to 
change your name and leave the capital.</font>

97
00:06:57,500 --> 00:06:59,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">O-Oh...</font>

98
00:06:59,830 --> 00:07:05,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And exposing treason is worth 
a reward of up to 1,000 rean.</font>

99
00:07:05,350 --> 00:07:09,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll add another zero to 
that out of my own pocket.</font>

100
00:07:09,410 --> 00:07:12,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? Wh-Why would you 
give me so much money?</font>

101
00:07:12,890 --> 00:07:15,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because you saved my father's life.</font>

102
00:07:17,320 --> 00:07:20,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I could return you to the Department
of the Imperial Household</font>

103
00:07:20,380 --> 00:07:23,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">as a member of my household,
but I want to hear what <i>you</i> want.</font>

104
00:07:24,440 --> 00:07:25,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Incredible...</font>

105
00:07:26,430 --> 00:07:29,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You are my master for life.</font>

106
00:07:29,810 --> 00:07:33,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No matter where I go, I will 
obey your every command.</font>

107
00:07:33,360 --> 00:07:34,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see.</font>

108
00:07:36,830 --> 00:07:38,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Zoey, you heard that, yes?</font>

109
00:07:38,720 --> 00:07:40,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes.</font>

110
00:07:40,310 --> 00:07:43,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your mother is no longer in danger.</font>

111
00:07:43,130 --> 00:07:45,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tell her she can rest at ease.</font>

112
00:07:45,060 --> 00:07:48,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master, you even
remembered my mother...</font>

113
00:07:49,270 --> 00:07:50,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you so much.</font>

114
00:07:58,750 --> 00:08:02,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}This is the capital of 
a nation of warriors,</font>

115
00:08:01,030 --> 00:08:02,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master?</font>

116
00:08:02,260 --> 00:08:06,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}but I have yet to see anyone 
who looks like a warrior!</font>

117
00:08:03,310 --> 00:08:06,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It sounds like something interesting 
is going on over there.</font>

118
00:08:10,500 --> 00:08:13,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well? Is there anyone who 
wishes to challenge me?</font>

119
00:08:13,870 --> 00:08:16,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All you need to do is fight me and win.</font>

120
00:08:16,540 --> 00:08:18,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The entry fee is three rean.</font>

121
00:08:18,470 --> 00:08:20,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And what do we get if we win?</font>

122
00:08:20,620 --> 00:08:21,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me.</font>

123
00:08:21,960 --> 00:08:25,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be your wife, your mistress, your 
servant, whatever you tell me to be.</font>

124
00:08:26,190 --> 00:08:28,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In imperial law, illegal 
slave-trading is defined as</i></font>

125
00:08:28,200 --> 00:08:30,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"the buying and selling of other people."</i></font>

126
00:08:31,320 --> 00:08:34,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Selling oneself doesn't 
violate that, but...</i></font>

127
00:08:34,370 --> 00:08:36,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So I just gotta defeat you, right?</font>

128
00:08:36,490 --> 00:08:39,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, but it has to be one-on-one.</font>

129
00:08:39,120 --> 00:08:41,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was my intention from the start.</font>

130
00:08:41,030 --> 00:08:45,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Otherwise, even if I won, 
I'd have to share you!</font>

131
00:08:51,120 --> 00:08:52,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Three rean.</font>

132
00:08:52,450 --> 00:08:53,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

133
00:08:53,750 --> 00:08:56,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You didn't pay the entry fee.</font>

134
00:08:56,020 --> 00:08:57,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oof, that's embarrassing!</font>

135
00:08:57,710 --> 00:09:00,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He challenged her without paying 
and lost within seconds!</font>

136
00:09:00,210 --> 00:09:01,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn it!</font>

137
00:09:01,360 --> 00:09:03,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, who's next?</font>

138
00:09:03,970 --> 00:09:05,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That'll be me!</font>

139
00:09:05,130 --> 00:09:06,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then I'm after him!</font>

140
00:09:06,330 --> 00:09:07,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I'm after him!</font>

141
00:09:13,480 --> 00:09:16,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow! That's fifteen challengers down!</font>

142
00:09:18,290 --> 00:09:19,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, who's next?</font>

143
00:09:19,740 --> 00:09:21,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-You do it.</font>

144
00:09:21,790 --> 00:09:22,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No way, man.</font>

145
00:09:25,200 --> 00:09:26,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll do it.</font>

146
00:09:26,970 --> 00:09:28,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, you need to pay.</font>

147
00:09:28,720 --> 00:09:30,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There'll be no need for that.</font>

148
00:09:30,780 --> 00:09:33,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">'Cause I'm gonna be the one... to win!</font>

149
00:09:43,350 --> 00:09:44,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What just happened?</font>

150
00:09:44,960 --> 00:09:46,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He beat her that easily...</font>

151
00:09:47,290 --> 00:09:49,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now you belong to me.</font>

152
00:09:49,460 --> 00:09:50,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hold it.</font>

153
00:09:51,450 --> 00:09:54,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That has to be against the rules.</font>

154
00:09:54,310 --> 00:09:55,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

155
00:09:55,390 --> 00:09:58,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's your deal, kid? 
Quit griping about—</font>

156
00:09:58,230 --> 00:10:00,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You used some sort of 
numbing drug, didn't you?</font>

157
00:10:00,700 --> 00:10:03,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you made someone else 
do that, it's two-on-one.</font>

158
00:10:04,710 --> 00:10:06,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What are you talking about?!</font>

159
00:10:06,890 --> 00:10:08,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where's your proof that—</font>

160
00:10:13,830 --> 00:10:15,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Found him.</font>

161
00:10:15,120 --> 00:10:17,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I don't know that guy!</font>

162
00:10:17,350 --> 00:10:20,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't lie, Chad!
That's your henchman, Rob!</font>

163
00:10:20,670 --> 00:10:22,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You were just drinking with 
him at my bar yesterday!</font>

164
00:10:22,980 --> 00:10:25,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Put the girl down, you coward!</font>

165
00:10:27,310 --> 00:10:31,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Little brat! You'll pay for butting in!</font>

166
00:10:43,060 --> 00:10:44,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just look at him now!</font>

167
00:10:44,890 --> 00:10:46,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That kid's incredible!</font>

168
00:10:46,540 --> 00:10:48,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He was so fast, I didn't see a thing!</font>

169
00:10:48,380 --> 00:10:49,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you want to continue?</font>

170
00:10:50,530 --> 00:10:53,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Y-Y...</font>

171
00:10:53,610 --> 00:10:56,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're gonna pay for this!</font>

172
00:10:55,180 --> 00:10:58,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}W-Wait for me, Chad!</font>

173
00:11:03,620 --> 00:11:05,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you awake now?</font>

174
00:11:07,120 --> 00:11:09,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who are... you?</font>

175
00:11:09,090 --> 00:11:12,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You ought to be grateful to this boy.</font>

176
00:11:12,200 --> 00:11:14,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He saved your life, you know.</font>

177
00:11:14,940 --> 00:11:16,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He did?</font>

178
00:11:16,260 --> 00:11:18,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How much do you remember?</font>

179
00:11:18,210 --> 00:11:22,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I remember... fighting with some creep...</font>

180
00:11:22,250 --> 00:11:24,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and suddenly, my legs 
wouldn't move anymore.</font>

181
00:11:24,790 --> 00:11:26,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He had his friend attack you.</font>

182
00:11:27,390 --> 00:11:28,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That coward!</font>

183
00:11:28,550 --> 00:11:31,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't deny that, but you 
were also too careless.</font>

184
00:11:32,620 --> 00:11:35,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why were you out there 
doing that, anyway?</font>

185
00:11:35,300 --> 00:11:36,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tell me.</font>

186
00:11:38,560 --> 00:11:41,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I ran out of money...</font>

187
00:11:41,700 --> 00:11:45,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I came here for the 
knight selection exam,</font>

188
00:11:45,090 --> 00:11:47,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I didn't make the cut.</font>

189
00:11:47,190 --> 00:11:50,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't even have the money 
to go home... so I...</font>

190
00:11:50,240 --> 00:11:52,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait. That doesn't make sense.</font>

191
00:11:52,400 --> 00:11:54,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What doesn't make sense?!</font>

192
00:11:54,340 --> 00:11:56,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I saw your skills back there.</font>

193
00:11:56,750 --> 00:11:58,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You couldn't have failed.</font>

194
00:11:58,810 --> 00:12:01,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I didn't agree with it either, 
so I looked into it.</font>

195
00:12:02,040 --> 00:12:06,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But then this year's head judge, 
the Tenth Prince, summoned me</font>

196
00:12:06,470 --> 00:12:09,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and said he'd be willing 
to let me progress...</font>

197
00:12:10,260 --> 00:12:12,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but in return, as a woman, I'd have to...</font>

198
00:12:12,340 --> 00:12:15,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, that's enough. I understand.</font>

199
00:12:15,710 --> 00:12:18,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That particular brother 
is the type to say that.</i></font>

200
00:12:19,240 --> 00:12:20,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you still want to be a knight?</font>

201
00:12:20,990 --> 00:12:22,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course!</font>

202
00:12:22,110 --> 00:12:25,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even if it takes years, I'll 
become a knight on my own merit!</font>

203
00:12:26,160 --> 00:12:28,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then you don't need to return home.</font>

204
00:12:29,190 --> 00:12:30,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here's 100 rean.</font>

205
00:12:30,690 --> 00:12:34,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It should be enough to live on until 
the next knight selection exam.</font>

206
00:12:34,060 --> 00:12:34,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wha...</font>

207
00:12:35,740 --> 00:12:38,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gigi, see to her living arrangements.</font>

208
00:12:38,680 --> 00:12:39,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Understood.</font>

209
00:12:39,980 --> 00:12:43,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What is this about? Why do all this?</font>

210
00:12:43,430 --> 00:12:45,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because I like you.</font>

211
00:12:45,930 --> 00:12:49,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You want recognition not for your 
womanhood, but based on merit.</font>

212
00:12:49,620 --> 00:12:51,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I like that sort of person.</font>

213
00:12:51,890 --> 00:12:55,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who are you? You're not just some kid.</font>

214
00:12:55,710 --> 00:12:56,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There he is!</font>

215
00:12:58,280 --> 00:12:59,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's the brat!</font>

216
00:12:59,550 --> 00:13:02,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You had some nerve 
humiliating me back there!</font>

217
00:13:02,460 --> 00:13:04,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Boss, you tell 'em, too!</font>

218
00:13:04,420 --> 00:13:05,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're—</font>

219
00:13:05,610 --> 00:13:06,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Stay back.</font>

220
00:13:10,290 --> 00:13:11,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh?</i></font>

221
00:13:11,740 --> 00:13:13,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You want to do the honors?</i></font>

222
00:13:13,680 --> 00:13:16,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Then I'll link you with 
my armor ring and...</i></font>

223
00:13:18,580 --> 00:13:19,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There.</font>

224
00:13:23,250 --> 00:13:26,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What the hell?!
His fists are on fire!</font>

225
00:13:26,170 --> 00:13:28,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've never seen anything 
like that before!</font>

226
00:13:28,360 --> 00:13:30,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey! No chickening out! Get him!</font>

227
00:13:40,780 --> 00:13:42,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">R-Rob!</font>

228
00:13:57,160 --> 00:13:59,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow... No wasted movements at all...</font>

229
00:13:59,850 --> 00:14:01,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's <i>that</i> strong?</font>

230
00:14:03,250 --> 00:14:04,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're not going to fight?</font>

231
00:14:04,720 --> 00:14:06,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's the Tenth Prince's knight!</font>

232
00:14:07,810 --> 00:14:10,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah. I get it now.</font>

233
00:14:11,780 --> 00:14:15,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">P-P-P-Please forgive me,
Thirteenth Prince!</font>

234
00:14:16,570 --> 00:14:19,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I get that they were paid 
under the table to do this,</i></font>

235
00:14:19,890 --> 00:14:21,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but once they knew who I was,</i></font>

236
00:14:21,750 --> 00:14:24,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>they thought they could avoid 
getting caught if they kept quiet.</i></font>

237
00:14:24,980 --> 00:14:27,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thirteenth... Prince?</font>

238
00:14:28,450 --> 00:14:32,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the Wise Prince,
the minister-prince of justice?!</font>

239
00:14:32,020 --> 00:14:34,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes. Noah Ararat.</font>

240
00:14:36,160 --> 00:14:37,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The real deal?</i></font>

241
00:14:37,280 --> 00:14:41,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Well, that would explain 
everything that's happened.</i></font>

242
00:14:41,410 --> 00:14:43,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's a prince and a minister,</i></font>

243
00:14:43,230 --> 00:14:45,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but he doesn't flaunt his status at all.</i></font>

244
00:14:45,870 --> 00:14:48,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll let you handle their punishment.</font>

245
00:14:49,100 --> 00:14:51,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you try to attack me?</font>

246
00:14:53,120 --> 00:14:56,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll let you off the hook 
just this once. Take them.</font>

247
00:14:56,020 --> 00:14:57,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Y-Yes, Your Highness!</font>

248
00:14:58,440 --> 00:15:00,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, get moving!</font>

249
00:15:04,430 --> 00:15:07,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What an impressive boy you are.</font>

250
00:15:07,180 --> 00:15:09,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your looks and skills are both top-notch.</font>

251
00:15:10,390 --> 00:15:12,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Who is he?</i></font>

252
00:15:12,010 --> 00:15:15,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't often see such 
remarkable young men.</font>

253
00:15:17,180 --> 00:15:18,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The Golden Gourd?</i></font>

254
00:15:19,940 --> 00:15:23,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I just recently learned 
about that and its owner!</i></font>

255
00:15:26,140 --> 00:15:27,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It is an honor to meet you,</font>

256
00:15:29,750 --> 00:15:31,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Imperial Highness 
the Lightning Prince.</font>

257
00:15:31,690 --> 00:15:34,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah, so you know who I am.</font>

258
00:15:34,480 --> 00:15:36,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that guy a prince, too?</font>

259
00:15:36,720 --> 00:15:39,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel like I've heard 
that name before...</font>

260
00:15:40,380 --> 00:15:43,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The Lightning Prince, Indra Ararat.</i></font>

261
00:15:44,340 --> 00:15:47,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A few decades ago, when the current 
emperor assumed the throne,</i></font>

262
00:15:48,410 --> 00:15:52,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>he stood in the center of 
power as the Prince Regent.</i></font>

263
00:15:52,400 --> 00:15:56,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The empire was in chaos because 
the emperor was so young,</i></font>

264
00:15:57,400 --> 00:16:00,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but he proved capable enough 
to take control of it all.</i></font>

265
00:16:00,960 --> 00:16:03,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Five years later, the Prince 
Regent stepped aside,</i></font>

266
00:16:03,820 --> 00:16:06,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>choosing to retire to his 
fief without argument...</i></font>

267
00:16:07,230 --> 00:16:14,410
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#f6f6f6"><font face="Times New Roman"><font size="32"><b>Lightning</b></font></font></font></font>

268
00:16:07,700 --> 00:16:11,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and he earned the title of 
"Lightning" for his role</i></font>

269
00:16:11,150 --> 00:16:13,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>in ushering in the emperor's 
new administration.</i></font>

270
00:16:14,730 --> 00:16:19,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And now such a great man suddenly 
shows up in the capital?</i></font>

271
00:16:19,460 --> 00:16:21,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come over here and sit down.</font>

272
00:16:21,670 --> 00:16:23,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you, Your Highness.</font>

273
00:16:23,290 --> 00:16:28,150
<font size="20">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#0b0700">Episode 10</font></b></font></font>

274
00:16:23,290 --> 00:16:28,150
<font size="20">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#0b0700">Lightning Prince and Wise Prince</font></b></font></font>

275
00:16:28,550 --> 00:16:31,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since you know who I am...</font>

276
00:16:31,510 --> 00:16:35,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I assume the emperor has 
already spoken to you.</font>

277
00:16:35,680 --> 00:16:37,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, he spoke to me himself.</font>

278
00:16:37,900 --> 00:16:42,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see, I see. Then you also 
know why I've come here.</font>

279
00:16:43,200 --> 00:16:45,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To evaluate me?</font>

280
00:16:45,690 --> 00:16:49,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The emperor chose you 
because he trusts you,</font>

281
00:16:49,340 --> 00:16:52,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so there's really no need for 
me to verify anything...</font>

282
00:16:52,320 --> 00:16:55,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but this does affect the life 
of my granddaughter, after all.</font>

283
00:16:55,680 --> 00:17:00,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The way he speaks would 
make an inspector furious.</i></font>

284
00:17:00,120 --> 00:17:06,290
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="18"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#565146">Emperor</font></b></font></font></font>

285
00:17:00,120 --> 00:17:06,290
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#ebebe9">m 0 0 l 75 0 75 15 0 15</font></font>

286
00:17:00,120 --> 00:17:06,290
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="10"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#565146">Uncle 
(Lightning Prince) 
<font size="12">Indra</font></font></b></font></font></font>

287
00:17:00,120 --> 00:17:06,290
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#ebebe9">m 0 0 l 75 0 75 15 0 15</font></font>

288
00:17:00,120 --> 00:17:06,290
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="10"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#565146">Brother 
<font size="12">Graeme</font></font></b></font></font></font>

289
00:17:00,120 --> 00:17:06,290
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#ebebe9">m 0 0 l 75 0 75 15 0 15</font></font>

290
00:17:00,410 --> 00:17:03,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Although he is the emperor's 
uncle, he remains his subject.</i></font>

291
00:17:01,100 --> 00:17:06,290
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#ebebe9">m 0 0 l 75 0 75 15 0 15</font></font>

292
00:17:01,890 --> 00:17:06,290
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="10"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#565146">Fourth Prince 
<font size="12">Henry</font></font></b></font></font></font>

293
00:17:01,990 --> 00:17:06,290
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="10"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#565146">Third Prince 
<font size="12">Kiro</font></font></b></font></font></font>

294
00:17:01,990 --> 00:17:06,290
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#ebebe9">m 0 0 l 75 0 75 15 0 15</font></font>

295
00:17:02,700 --> 00:17:06,290
<font size="20">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><b><font size="15"><font color="#38392a">(Subjects)</font></font></b></font></font>

296
00:17:02,750 --> 00:17:06,290
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="10"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#565146">First Prince 
<font size="12">Gilbert</font></font></b></font></font></font>

297
00:17:02,750 --> 00:17:06,290
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#ebebe9">m 0 0 l 75 0 75 15 0 15</font></font>

298
00:17:02,750 --> 00:17:06,290
<font size="20">{\an8}<font size="10"><font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#565146">Crown Prince,
Second Prince 
<font size="12">Albert</font></font></b></font></font></font>

299
00:17:02,750 --> 00:17:06,290
<font size="20">{\an8}<font color="#ebebe9">m 0 0 l 75 0 75 15 0 15</font></font>

300
00:17:03,170 --> 00:17:06,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>For him to simply address him as "the 
emperor" is extremely disrespectful.</i></font>

301
00:17:07,460 --> 00:17:11,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But... well, I don't think he'd even 
care if I called him out on it.</i></font>

302
00:17:11,670 --> 00:17:13,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't think my father would 
find fault with him, either.</i></font>

303
00:17:14,470 --> 00:17:17,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's just how this man is.</i></font>

304
00:17:18,000 --> 00:17:21,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What will you do if I don't 
measure up to your standards?</font>

305
00:17:22,600 --> 00:17:25,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I just won't let you 
marry her, that's all.</font>

306
00:17:25,220 --> 00:17:27,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But this was an imperial 
command, was it not?</font>

307
00:17:27,070 --> 00:17:28,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That doesn't mean a thing.</font>

308
00:17:28,680 --> 00:17:32,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure, if it were any other order from 
the emperor, I'd obey at any cost.</font>

309
00:17:32,980 --> 00:17:36,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But this is my granddaughter, you know.</font>

310
00:17:37,280 --> 00:17:40,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is my precious little 
granddaughter we're talking about.</font>

311
00:17:40,510 --> 00:17:43,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That means it's not political.
It's personal.</font>

312
00:17:43,990 --> 00:17:48,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And the one who gave the order is my 
nephew, the boy I once bounced on my knee.</font>

313
00:17:49,120 --> 00:17:52,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If he's wrong, I'll smack him upside the 
head if that's what it takes to stop him.</font>

314
00:17:52,770 --> 00:17:55,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I see. He's an interesting man.</i></font>

315
00:17:56,160 --> 00:17:59,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't think he has any 
desire to gain power.</i></font>

316
00:17:59,050 --> 00:18:01,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's why he doesn't get 
rebuked for being rude.</i></font>

317
00:18:01,590 --> 00:18:03,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In fact, this is preferred.</i></font>

318
00:18:03,400 --> 00:18:05,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So... do I pass?</font>

319
00:18:06,530 --> 00:18:09,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what I'm about to find out.</font>

320
00:18:10,160 --> 00:18:14,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What is this? It feels like 
something's crushing me...</i></font>

321
00:18:14,560 --> 00:18:17,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's just like what I make Leviathan do!</i></font>

322
00:18:18,150 --> 00:18:19,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The menace!</i></font>

323
00:18:21,140 --> 00:18:22,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In that case...</i></font>

324
00:18:22,370 --> 00:18:24,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll push back!</i></font>

325
00:18:24,330 --> 00:18:25,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh?</font>

326
00:18:26,410 --> 00:18:28,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Good! Now, with one blow...</i></font>

327
00:18:28,930 --> 00:18:30,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>No, I shouldn't.</i></font>

328
00:18:31,110 --> 00:18:35,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's my great-uncle and, potentially, 
my future grandfather-in-law.</i></font>

329
00:18:35,710 --> 00:18:38,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I shouldn't injure him in public.</i></font>

330
00:18:38,460 --> 00:18:42,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll control this so I 
neither win nor lose.</i></font>

331
00:18:45,290 --> 00:18:48,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Impressive, boy! I admit defeat!</font>

332
00:18:48,930 --> 00:18:51,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um... I thought it was a draw...</font>

333
00:18:51,660 --> 00:18:52,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, blockhead.</font>

334
00:18:52,930 --> 00:18:57,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You read my technique perfectly 
and <i>made</i> it a draw.</font>

335
00:18:57,400 --> 00:18:59,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your mindfulness did me in.</font>

336
00:19:00,420 --> 00:19:04,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He calls it mindfulness,
but he gave it away himself.</i></font>

337
00:19:04,490 --> 00:19:06,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He really is the type of person 
you just can't dislike.</i></font>

338
00:19:07,750 --> 00:19:09,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I like you, boy.</font>

339
00:19:09,710 --> 00:19:12,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take care of my granddaughter.</font>

340
00:19:12,320 --> 00:19:13,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I will.</font>

341
00:19:14,930 --> 00:19:16,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm in a good mood today!</font>

342
00:19:16,710 --> 00:19:18,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You there!</font>

343
00:19:18,450 --> 00:19:20,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bring out all the booze you've got!</font>

344
00:19:21,210 --> 00:19:22,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This round's on me!</font>

345
00:19:23,040 --> 00:19:25,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone who can drink, drink up!</font>

346
00:19:27,230 --> 00:19:29,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Could he be any more extravagant?</i></font>

347
00:19:29,720 --> 00:19:32,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He sure isn't like any 
of the nobles I know.</i></font>

348
00:19:32,850 --> 00:19:34,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is yours.</font>

349
00:19:34,230 --> 00:19:35,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">An engagement gift.</font>

350
00:19:35,710 --> 00:19:36,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A ring?</font>

351
00:19:36,880 --> 00:19:38,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That there is...</font>

352
00:19:38,510 --> 00:19:40,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Show me your strength.</i></font>

353
00:19:46,480 --> 00:19:47,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is this place?</font>

354
00:19:57,370 --> 00:20:00,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Show me your strength," you say?</font>

355
00:20:10,590 --> 00:20:11,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Send it flying!</font>

356
00:20:27,410 --> 00:20:31,870
<font size="20">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#fdfffd">Earth</font></b></font></font>

357
00:20:27,410 --> 00:20:31,870
<font size="20">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#fdfffd">Light</font></b></font></font>

358
00:20:27,410 --> 00:20:31,870
<font size="20">{\an8}<font face="Times New Roman"><b><font color="#fdfffd">Dark</font></b></font></font>

359
00:20:28,710 --> 00:20:30,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It went up.</font>

360
00:20:30,360 --> 00:20:31,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Light has a +C.</font>

361
00:20:32,280 --> 00:20:34,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My name is Behemoth.</i></font>

362
00:20:35,680 --> 00:20:37,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I surrender to you.</i></font>

363
00:20:42,510 --> 00:20:44,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's called Behemoth.</font>

364
00:20:44,490 --> 00:20:46,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Its power pairs with mine.</font>

365
00:20:46,580 --> 00:20:47,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like this?</font>

366
00:20:57,920 --> 00:21:02,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even I couldn't win Behemoth over, 
and you did it in a heartbeat!</font>

367
00:21:02,540 --> 00:21:06,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Even a man as powerful as Your 
Highness couldn't win it over?</font>

368
00:21:06,110 --> 00:21:09,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It only told me its name.</font>

369
00:21:09,070 --> 00:21:14,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was hoping I'd get to see that 
fantastical golden figure again.</font>

370
00:21:14,510 --> 00:21:17,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Its figure? Like this?</font>

371
00:21:20,880 --> 00:21:22,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah! That's it!</font>

372
00:21:22,590 --> 00:21:26,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can do that, too?
You're really something, boy!</font>

373
00:21:26,280 --> 00:21:30,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can learn powers and abilities 
by making it battle.</font>

374
00:21:30,150 --> 00:21:32,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Make it battle what?</font>

375
00:21:32,830 --> 00:21:34,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well...</font>

376
00:21:34,220 --> 00:21:36,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think it'd be faster to just show you.</font>

377
00:21:39,210 --> 00:21:41,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The magic sword of water, Leviathan.</i></font>

378
00:21:42,070 --> 00:21:44,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The ring of flame, Luthier.</i></font>

379
00:21:45,040 --> 00:21:47,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The painting of wind, Huwawa.</i></font>

380
00:21:48,060 --> 00:21:50,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The ring of earth, Behemoth.</i></font>

381
00:21:50,760 --> 00:21:54,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It has been a thousand years 
since they were all assembled...</i></font>

382
00:21:54,040 --> 00:21:56,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>not since the Silver Age.</i></font>

383
00:21:56,950 --> 00:21:59,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And the Thirteenth Prince...</i></font>

384
00:22:01,340 --> 00:22:05,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yes, he was about to have 
a wondrous experience</i></font>

385
00:22:05,170 --> 00:22:08,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>that could only be called a miracle.</i></font>

386
